data.description: Put this home on your Christmas list!!  Beautifully updated ranch home sitting on almost 2-acres of land is a must see!  Driving up you will notice the quaint rocking chair front porch which is perfect for sipping your morning coffee or chatting with family or friends.  Entering the living area, you will see the newly installed LVP flooring in all living areas, crown molding, and a wood burning fireplace perfect for chilly evenings.  There is plenty of room to entertain in the spacious eat-in kitchen.  From the newly installed quartz countertops, beautiful tile backsplash, new stainless-steel appliances that convey with the property, stainless-steel farmhouse sink, newly painted cabinets and farmhouse door that opens to the laundry room means you can begin entertaining immediately. There are two doors in the kitchen that lead to the covered deck for additional entertainment space. The primary bedroom is off the living area while the other two bedrooms are located on the opposite side of the home. The attached bathroom in the primary bedrooms has recently been updated as well as the bathroom located next to the two additional bedrooms.  New carpet was installed this month in the two guest bedrooms. There are two storage/outbuildings that will convey with the sale of the home. New HVAC was installed in 2022 and the roof was installed in 2014. This home is totally move-in ready and USDA 100% financing is available to qualified buyers.  Schedule an appointment today to see this charming home.
